tariffs

Class ContractTariff

  • java.lang.Object
    • tariffs.Tariff
      • tariffs.ContractTariff

  • public class ContractTariff
extends Tariff
    A Tariff subclass that represents corporate tariffs. It contains additional fields 'dailyMinutes' and 'abroadCalls' and their getters/setters.
